# Bundlekit

Use when authoring or validating design bundles (`*.bundle.yaml`), legacy dynamics YAML, or design MD render on a docs hub.

## Tools

- `bundle_split` · `bundle_merge` · `bundle_check` · `bundle_split_all` · `bundle_normalize`
- `docs_render` · `docs_render_common`
- `legacy_dynamics_validate`

## Owned skills

`/spec` · `/update-spec` · `/update-spec-legacy` · `/legacy-spec` · `/bqa-grill-docs`

## Accelerators (optional)

- Hubdocs: resolve CMP/CTR/FLOW IDs
- ArtifactGraph: tags/parity slices
- Missing accelerator never blocks Bundlekit tools
